==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|china|men}}

#{{cattag|obsolete|pejorative}} A [[Chinese]] [[person]]
#{{Cricket}} A [[left arm unorthodox]] [[spin bowler]]
#{{Cricket}} A [[ball]], bowled by a left arm unorthodox spin bowler, with the [[wrist]] [[action]] of a [[leg break]], but which [[spin]]s from [[off]] to [[leg]] for a [[right handed]] [[batsman]]
#{{Cricket}} Or, [[conversely]], such a ball bowled with the action of a [[googly]].

====Usage notes====
Two of the cricket definitions (3 and 4) are inconsistent, but both are used.

